Package: reliant-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         elementary-icon-theme
Description: Reliant icon theme
 An icon theme based on elementary with a more classic approach

Package: reliant-metacity-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Reliant metacity theme
 A metacity theme reminiscent of the classic clearlooks style of old

Package: reliant-gtk-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         mate-themes
Description: Reliant gtk theme
 Minor tweaks to the BlueMenta GTK theme from MATE

Package: reliant-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         reliant-icon-theme,
         reliant-metacity-theme,
         reliant-gtk-theme
Description: Reliant desktop theme
 A Desktop theme incorporating the reliant metacity and icon themes

Package: reliant-theme-dark
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         reliant-icon-theme,
         marco-common,
         gnome-themes-extra,
         adwaita-qt
Description: Reliant (Dark) desktop theme
 A Desktop theme incorporating the reliant icon theme with a dark window style

